= Language.C =

Parser and Pretty Printer for C99.
See http://www.sivity.net/projects/language.c/

== Build ==

The following configure flags are available:
 deriveData ... derive Data.Generics and Typeable instances

runhaskell Setup configure
runhaskell Setup build
-- or --
cabal configure
cabal build

Provide the set of flags passing
 --flags="<flags-seperated-by-space>"
to configure.

== Testing ==

=== parse-and-print ===

> cd test
> make c_test
> ./bin/CTest -I/usr/src/yarv /usr/src/yarv/vm.c

